            . I am a <rs id="t18270913-173-viclabel983" type="occupation">tailor</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-173-victim1696 t18270913-173-viclabel983"></join>, and live in Monmouth-street. On Saturday last I offered this waistcoat for sale to a man in the street - while I was in conversation with him the prisoner came up and took it from me; he ran, and I followed him, and cried Stop-thief! his companions came across him, and took it from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-173-person1698">
