            . I heard a noise and went out - I took the prisoner into custody. The prosecutor was standing by him- he said, at the watch-house, that if I would go with him to a certain court in the Strand, I might, perhaps, find the waistcoat.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-173-person1699">
