            . I am an officer. I was in Broad-street; I saw the prisoner running, and the prosecutor after him - I stopped the prisoner, but saw no waistcoat on him.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 24.</p>
